# Excel Reporting Standards

## Workbook Integrity & UX
- **Data Mutability:** Do not overwrite or mutate pipeline data (`main_data`) inside the reporter layer. Treat dictionaries as read-only.
- **Sanitization:** All string cell values MUST be sanitized to prevent CSV/Excel injection (strip leading `=`, `+`, `-`, `@`).
- **Formatting:** Ensure Ghost Pane guards are active to freeze top rows. The Table of Contents (TOC) naming must exactly match the tab names.
- **Conditional Logic:** The 'Action Required' column in the Content Hub must strictly trigger "Needs Copy" red conditional formatting when populated. Do not pass `None` to action columns.